{"tid":1793704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[行動]入黎睇！一個真正經濟攬炒既平安夜 (新開)","createTime":"2019-12-22T14:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T12:09:30.000Z","uid":94771,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"efcec8bff17e7927d66f40e4acbc154bafc7c04b","tid":1793704,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ67pX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZ67pX4.jpg&h=7823285a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更新地點建議！五區商場！<br />\n<br />\n香港人自6月以來<br />\n走過烈日，步入深秋，迎接寒冬。終於迎來聖誕。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕將至，本來應該普天同慶，全城歡呼。但大家唔好忘記，呢一刻大家仲可以係香港過聖誕，唔駛被送中，係因為：<br />\n<br />\n-超過5000被捕義士<br />\n-數不清的暴動控罪<br />\n-直接被殺的周梓樂﹑陳彦霖<br />\n-無數被政權逼令自殺的烈士<br />\n-無數被羈押的手足<br />\n- 星火被指涉洗黑錢<br />\n<br />\n如果大家休息下來，安於逸樂。即係大啖大啖食緊人血饅頭！<br />\n<br />\n唔該香港人爭氣！今個平安夜行出來，一齊塞爆晒下面d商場！！<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月24日<br />\n時間：7pm至10pm<br />\n更新地點建議！五區商場！<br />\n<br />\n-新界：<br />\n沙田新城市<br />\n元朗YOHO<br />\n-九龍：<br />\n尖沙咀 海港城<br />\n旺角 朗豪坊<br />\n-港島：<br />\n銅鑼灣 時代廣場<br />\n<br />\n應承我，下年既聖誕，我地要同手足係煲底除罩慶祝！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n頻道:<a href=\"https://t.me/xmasevehkchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehkchannel&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=1da43eea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/xmasevehkchannel</a><br />\n公海：<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=690f4eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n連登post:<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789301</a><br />\n<br />\n真正屬於香港人既平安夜，需要每位手足<br />\n急！招人！<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScU7glbdBUt0V_b756eIol_24G9pdWmoMpV4T8NIEh-_neERg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScU7glbdBUt0V_b756eIol_24G9pdWmoMpV4T8NIEh-_neERg%2Fviewform&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=c3cd53a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScU7glbdBUt0V_b756eIol_24G9pdWmoMpV4T8NIEh-_neERg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n原POST<br />\n［行動post]入黎睇！一個真正經濟攬炒既平安夜<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782022</a>"},{"pid":"b9506c3d530f935cd02a5d6060fee386ebeb906c","tid":1793704,"uid":188685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:47:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.25 SUCK三部曲<br />\n12.31 和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1 元旦遊行<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#聖誕不消費<br />\n#中環PePe專門店=人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDF0J4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDF0J4E.jpg&h=82e3d3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJALVbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJALVbk.png&h=1cd9c1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dECa6h1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdECa6h1.png&h=00663094&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3rvmRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3rvmRm.jpg&h=f784f0be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3qzOwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3qzOwn.jpg&h=d2aa8131&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e34ae74db286beb4a8c78da9308227105ae4275d","tid":1793704,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16181e4421367d22ca71402b2e8fab957f6671e6","tid":1793704,"uid":103613,"like":0,"